**Best practices:**

- Set explicit pool sizes; don't use defaults
- Monitor thread count continuously
- Set queue capacity to prevent unlimited queuing
- Enable shutdown hooks: setWaitForTasksToCompleteOnShutdown(true)
- Use different thread pools for different purposes
- Profile under expected load in staging
- Log thread names for debugging
- Implement thread leak detection
